<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0143b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0143b0101">夫乾<note n="0143001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">巛＝坤【史】</note><app n="0143001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">坤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">巛</rdg></app>振<note n="0143002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30625"/>＝極【史】</note><app n="0143002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">極</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30625"/></rdg></app>。遂通三裁。<note n="0143003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30824"/>＝靈【史】</note><app n="0143003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">靈</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30824"/></rdg></app>像告徵。廓有開闢。覆載潤流。<note n="0143004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧉾＝蠢【史】</note><app n="0143004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蠢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧉾</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0143b02" type="honorific"/>茲犁庶。是以天生之民。樹之以君。非君無以里其民。非民
<lb ed="I" n="0143b03" type="honorific"/>無以顯其君。聲動嚮應。今故相承。是以干戈震動。出自非
<lb ed="I" n="0143b04" type="honorific"/>今。<note n="0143005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30825"/>＝堂【史】</note><app n="0143005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">堂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30825"/></rdg></app>堯至聖。尚致阪<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">泉</unclear>之師。周武之化。<note n="0143006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30478"/>＝亦【史】</note><app n="0143006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30478"/></rdg></app>興不期之<note n="0143007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30826"/>＝旅【史】</note><app n="0143007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旅</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30826"/></rdg></app>。是
<lb ed="I" n="0143b05" type="honorific"/>以黑太逋寇。假息<note n="0143008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">閞＝關【史】</note><app n="0143008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">關</lem><rdg wit="【原】">閞</rdg></app>壟。侯景拔扈。苟存江佐。鼠<note n="0143009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB06283"/>＝竊【史】</note><app n="0143009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">竊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB06283"/></rdg></app>之徒。敢
<lb ed="I" n="0143b06" type="honorific"/><note n="0143010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨶳＝窺【史】</note><app n="0143010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窺</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨶳</rdg></app>問鼎。今我大<note n="0143011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">斊＝齊【史】</note><app n="0143011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">齊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">斊</rdg></app>。咨天心如承主。廓四海以為居。坐太<app type="star" corresp="#0143002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">極</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30625"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0143b07" type="honorific"/>如壽禪。闇与契如同苻。巍巍乎以白日如並光。堂〃如無
<lb ed="I" n="0143b08" type="honorific"/>能名焉。若用梟禽二<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">虜</unclear>。必如指掌。未即誅<note n="0143012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30827"/>＝戮【史】</note><app n="0143012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戮</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30827"/></rdg></app>。寬侍歸順。是
<lb ed="I" n="0143b09" type="honorific"/>以廣□嚮豪。立為督將。弟相部鎮坊。茲醜豎邢多五十人
<lb ed="I" n="0143b10" type="honorific"/>等。昔因封而居。子孫留禺。今在肆土。為人領袖。其人可謂
<lb ed="I" n="0143b11" type="honorific"/>天資<note n="0143013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30708"/>＝傑【史】</note><app n="0143013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">傑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30708"/></rdg></app>邁。幹<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">飾</unclear>明□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">圓</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">弓</unclear>連<note n="0143014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䦢＝闊【史】</note><app n="0143014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">闊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䦢</rdg></app>。飛刀接刃。為帝所知。召國
<lb ed="I" n="0143b12" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">於</unclear>□武藝之士。實<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">自</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孤</unclear>絕一時。<note n="0143015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30828"/>＝寑【史】</note><app n="0143015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30828"/></rdg></app>蹇酋勇。<app type="star" corresp="#0143006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30478"/></rdg></app>難量者哉。遂
<lb ed="I" n="0143b13" type="honorific"/>在合州發弘<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear>願。願令軍侶行還。建□像一區。經營尋<note n="0143016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30829"/>＝就【史】</note><app n="0143016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30829"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0143b14" type="honorific"/>藉因斯福。咸　發上願。令　皇祚遐□。業化清熙。澤沾九
<lb ed="I" n="0143b15" type="honorific"/>區。恩過八<app type="star" corresp="#0143002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">極</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30625"/></rdg></app>。後令先<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">亡</unclear>現在。含情能<app type="star" corresp="#0143004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蠢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧉾</rdg></app>。同歸妙境。
<lb ed="I" n="0143b16" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">維</unclear>大<app type="star" corresp="#0143011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">齊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">斊</rdg></app>天保二年歲次辛未七月壬申朔十五日丙戌定</p>
